title: Supp LFP Gold/Plat
body:
I'm a Gold 4 supp, who is currently looking for good adc. My higest was Gold 1 in soloque and i would say that i play decent - good in (80%) of my games. 
I am 21 years old and i am looking for someone 18+ with the ambition to climb, a positie attitude and low to none lvl of tilt. 
Add me if ur interested:  CluesBlues
